    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      392.56,
      523.56,
      447.26
    ],
    "text": "On 09.09.2018, investigations were initiated by the Homicide and Organized Crime Investigation Division of the Criminal Investigation Department based on a complaint received by the Inspector General of Police regarding the abduction and disappearance of a retired Army soldier residing in Kirindiwela, Narangaspitiya.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      461.82,
      505.75,
      488.9
    ],
    "text": "Accordingly, on 08.06.2026, a suspect wanted in connection with this offence was arrested in the Ranpokunugama area within the Nittambuwa Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      503.46,
      493.18,
      516.74
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is a 47-year-old resident of the Ranpokunugama area, Nittambuwa.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      531.18,
      521.05,
      572.06
    ],
    "text": "During the arrest, the suspect was found in possession of a foreign-manufactured pen-type firearm, along with five rounds of ammunition, four T-56 cartridges, eight 9 mm cartridges, and two 12-bore cartridges.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      586.65,
      523.85,
      613.73
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by officers of the Homicide and Organized Crime Investigation Division of the Criminal Investigation Department.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
